Set SENTINEL to Q

Display Instructions Main Menu
    1 - Input Class Information
    2 - Display Class Information
    Q to Quit

Prompt user for menu choice
While menu choice is not equal to 1 or 2?
    Is menu choice Q?
        Display exit message
        Exit program
    Else    
        Display Error Message
        Prompt user for menu choice

If user choice == 1
    Display Instructions Class Input   
        Input class information
        Q to Quit

    Open text file for Appending information
    
    Prompt user for class code
    While class code does not match expected format
        Is class code Q
            Display exit message
            Exit program
        Else
            Display error message
            Prompt user for class code

    (Repeat for each element of class information)

    Append class information to file
